---
title: Carb Smart Harvest Fruit, Chicken and Bacon Salad with Feta and Walnuts
description: We've taken all your cheese board favourites and come up with a magnificent carb-smart salad! This meal has sweetness, crunch, saltiness and decadence all wrapped into one!

